show.title: My Handsome Bodyguard
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/ALW2fK
show.description: When Lea unexpectedly inherits her father's mafia empire, she refuses to play by the old rules. Determined to transform the family business, she makes bold, risky moves that send shockwaves through the criminal underworld—earning her powerful enemies, including her vengeful ex-fiancé Michael. As threats close in from all sides, Lea finds an unlikely ally in Ryan, the stoic, devastatingly handsome bodyguard assigned to protect her. What begins as a professional relationship soon ignites into something far more dangerous and passionate. Now, as Lea fights to cement her position in a world where women are never meant to lead, she discovers that her greatest vulnerability might be her growing feelings for the one man sworn to take a bullet for her—her handsome bodyguard.
